35
00:02:39,997 --> 00:02:42,497
What are you talking about?
Where are you?

36
00:02:43,167 --> 00:02:44,368
I will protect...

37
00:02:45,508 --> 00:02:47,008
the apartment.

38
00:02:47,077 --> 00:02:50,077
Sae Bom. Explain that to me again.
What do you...

39
