Hi. Your rice cakes are here.

46
00:03:38,687 --> 00:03:42,057
Here. Enjoy it and order more again.

47
00:03:43,398 --> 00:03:44,967
Are you a policeman too?

48
00:03:45,027 --> 00:03:46,027
How'd you know?

49
00:03:46,937 --> 00:03:48,198
Oh, you saw this?

50
00:03:49,467 --> 00:03:51,138
I'm not a weird guy.

51
00:03:51,208 --> 00:03:53,108
I'm your neighbour’s friend.

52
00:03:53,978 --> 00:03:55,638
Oh. You have two jobs?

53
00:03:56,238 --> 00:03:57,948
Why do you have your gun, then?

54
00:03:58,007 --> 00:04:01,277
It's so I can catch bad guys and take them away.

55
00:04:01,347 --> 00:04:04,287
People need to see this to know what I am.

56
00:04:04,347 --> 00:04:05,587
Can I see it up close?

57
00:04:05,648 --> 00:04:08,018
No, you can't. It's dangerous.

58
00:04:09,087 --> 00:04:12,627
To be honest with you,
I've never used it in my life.

59
00:04:12,687 --> 00:04:14,157
I just carry it around.

60
00:04:15,127 --> 00:04:16,728
It looks good, doesn't it?

61
00:04:20,238 --> 00:04:21,368
I'm home.

62
00:04:24,807 --> 00:04:26,007
Are you dead?

63
00:04:26,407 --> 00:04:28,777
