64
00:04:29,478 --> 00:04:31,148
Here's your hamburger.

65
00:04:31,678 --> 00:04:33,377
What? Oh, dear.

66
00:04:33,618 --> 00:04:36,216
You're getting up only
because I brought you food?

67
00:04:36,217 --> 00:04:38,687
- Gosh.
- Thank you.

68
00:04:39,787 --> 00:04:40,958
You said it was a hamburger.

69
00:04:41,287 --> 00:04:43,988
