What's the problem?

70
00:04:44,057 --> 00:04:45,888
If you don't want it, don't bother.

71
00:04:46,757 --> 00:04:49,858
Honey, I didn't say I wouldn't eat it.

72
00:04:49,928 --> 00:04:51,428
Your skin's cracking again?

73
00:04:51,497 --> 00:04:52,497
No.

74
00:04:53,467 --> 00:04:54,798
My gosh.

75
00:04:55,597 --> 00:04:58,437
You're old. Use hand cream and lotion.

76
00:04:58,507 --> 00:05:00,578
No, it's not because of that.

77
00:05:01,138 --> 00:05:03,407
I fell yesterday and sprained my wrist.

78
00:05:03,478 --> 00:05:05,078
That's nothing, then.

79
00:05:05,478 --> 00:05:08,577
Honey, if someone says they got hurt,

80
00:05:08,647 --> 00:05:11,088
don't you even want to know why?

81
00:05:12,918 --> 00:05:15,858
Fine. Did something happen to you?

82
00:05:15,988 --> 00:05:20,298
Yes. Yesterday, on the sixth floor.
You know...

83
00:05:20,457 --> 00:05:23,228
Mom! I have a meeting!
Why didn't you wake me?

84
00:05:23,968 --> 00:05:27,468
Hey. How would we know you had plans?

85
00:05:27,738 --> 00:05:29,137
Are we telepathic?

86
00:05:29,637 --> 00:05:31,868
Dong Hyun, do you want a sandwich?

87
00:05:32,538 --> 00:05:34,478
You eat all you want and live long lives.

88
00:05:34,538 --> 00:05:36,238
Hey, this is...

89
00:05:36,848 --> 00:05:38,576
He's such an obnoxious kid.

90
00:05:38,577 --> 00:05:42,077
My goodness...

91
