(I Made Money on YouTube!)

92
00:05:51,428 --> 00:05:52,757
My gosh.

93
00:05:57,397 --> 00:05:58,897
I have over 1,000 subscribers.

94
00:05:58,968 --> 00:06:01,538
I will turn a profit at this rate.

95
00:06:02,137 --> 00:06:04,007
Just cover the initial cost.

96
00:06:04,067 --> 00:06:05,408
Don't you trust me?

97
00:06:06,507 --> 00:06:09,338
Okay, fine. I'll be right there.

98
00:06:21,788 --> 00:06:24,088
Who parked like this? Mister.

99
