Why are the shutters down?

102
00:06:33,298 --> 00:06:34,767
Why aren't you moving?

103
00:06:34,838 --> 00:06:37,408
What is the matter? I'm dead busy.

104
00:06:37,468 --> 00:06:38,838
My schedule's messed up.

105
00:06:38,908 --> 00:06:40,108
Oh, come on!

106
